{"tid":1831969,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"逆權打油春聯","createTime":"2020-01-21T00:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T06:12:11.000Z","uid":344847,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1fdb5df8623d920791dbd84df46f9e353b78ce60","tid":1831969,"uid":344847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T00:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1zmO5y2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1zmO5y2.jpg&h=05b3e385&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fcAXesp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfcAXesp.jpg&h=a993a09d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/82gO5y4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F82gO5y4.jpg&h=6033bfe5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3APP0L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3APP0L.jpg&h=dd1c63fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AdcZsNr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAdcZsNr.jpg&h=67c4592c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7X6vzss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7X6vzss.jpg&h=2f35c9d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[url]<span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/647472862009944/posts/2666799716743905/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F647472862009944%2Fposts%2F2666799716743905%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV93T1AxqF%2FibzLHEE6598sd0%3D&h=8e88d8ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/647472862009944/posts/2666799716743905/?d=n</a></span>[/url]<br />\n<br />\n農曆新年傳統習俗之一是在家中和一些商店貼上揮春或是春聯，取個好意頭。可惜常用的揮春語句多流於俗套，春聯更難有新意，近年已經越來越少人會張貼。但今年香港潮流可不一樣。經歷過七個多月的逆權運動洗禮後，港人都寄望來年社會局勢會好轉。自然地，一些抗爭口號便可能成為揮春或是拜年賀詞。但抗爭還抗爭，畢竟新年流流仍應保持一點春節的氛圍。有見及此，筆者於是嘗試譜寫了一些另類春聯，以逆權運動為題再配以相關的賀歲詞以應節。儘管未能完全符合傳統對聯的嚴格要求，這些逆權「打油」春聯亦別具一番情趣，可以用來向大家拜年為港人打氣，也籍此對這塲社會運動作出年末回顧與反思。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">會意篇</span></span><br />\n<br />\n🔺光復香港 時代革命<br />\n🔻春回大地 萬象更新<br />\n<br />\n🔺光復香港<br />\n🔻時代革命<br />\n（橫批：迎春接福）<br />\n<br />\n🔺五大訴求  缺一不可<br />\n🔻百無禁忌  滿載而歸<br />\n<br />\n🔺五大訴求<br />\n🔻缺一不可<br />\n（橫批：五福臨門）<br />\n<br />\n🔺香港人加油<br />\n🔻庚子年得手<br />\n（橫批：五大訴求）<br />\n<br />\n🔺煲底相見<br />\n🔻出入平安<br />\n<br />\n🔺上善若水<br />\n🔻至誠逾金<br />\n（橫批：招財進寶）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">超人篇</span></span><br />\n<br />\n🔺網開一面<br />\n🔻遍地開花<br />\n（撗批：花開四季）<br />\n<br />\n🔺黃台之瓜  何堪再摘<br />\n🔻藍絲之昃  何已完瓜<br />\n（橫批：喜氣洋洋）<br />\n<br />\n🔺最好的因可成最壞的果<br />\n🔻最強的國可成最裂的家<br />\n（橫批：國泰民安）<br />\n<br />\n🔺因果由國<br />\n🔻容港治己<br />\n（橫批：萬事勝意）<br />\n<br />\n🔺因果由國  容港治己<br />\n🔻萬事勝意  心想事成<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">榮光篇</span></span><br />\n<br />\n🔺光復香港  榮光共創<br />\n🔻時代革命  義憤民誠<br />\n（橫批：運轉福星）<br />\n<br />\n🔺嘉誠十億應急情<br />\n🔻功德無量化窩心<br />\n（橫批：香港有李）<br />\n<br />\n🔺光復氣侯  拯救地球<br />\n🔻光復香港  還我自由<br />\n（橫批：春回大地）<br />\n<br />\n🔺時代風雲  一支獨秀<br />\n🔻時代革命  五大訴求<br />\n（橫批：萬象更新）<br />\n<br />\n🔺衝衝子勇武挑時代<br />\n🔻段爸爸崇智躋風雲<br />\n（橫批：鯉躍龍門）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">勇武篇</span></span><br />\n<br />\n🔺巴打逆權烹走狗<br />\n🔻絲打傲雪揭色狼<br />\n（橫批：佳偶天成）<br />\n<br />\n🔺傲雪凌霜曙光乍現  帶來新希望<br />\n🔻逆權抗暴暗渡鴻溝  闖出再生天<br />\n（橫批：柳暗花明）<br />\n<br />\n🔺月娥飆歌唱祖國<br />\n🔻兆波無語黨中央<br />\n（橫批：龍鳳呈祥）<br />\n<br />\n🔺涼雞拼社運無得輸<br />\n🔻細頸瓶貿戰無得贏<br />\n（橫批：賭運亨通）"},{"pid":"36ec3f83eeec63b3d41bf0946b6d35ac9489ab20","tid":1831969,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T01:07:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328a3d2bb16ae03569e2ef3d3038937cd1a1b364","tid":1831969,"uid":133341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T01:11:58.000Z","msg":"巴打手字好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6db61a3938b9ed21261ae373173b0f35a008d3e","tid":1831969,"uid":72696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T01:19:18.000Z","msg":"春聯係蝗語，香港叫開揮春"},{"pid":"c4f782c985252465d9d59e4fdd23b3c6238a8458","tid":1831969,"uid":312858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T01:25:59.000Z","msg":"一人一句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鼠年光復百業<br />\n子歲香港封登"},{"pid":"6471ac28cae555951ded61acac17a023a2622fe7","tid":1831969,"uid":344847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6db61a3938b9ed21261ae373173b0f35a008d3e","tid":1831969,"uid":72696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T01:19:18.000Z","msg":"春聯係蝗語，香港叫開揮春"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T01:26:59.000Z","msg":"揮春通常是四字詞語，春聯是對聯，要符合平仄對仗格式。唔係蝗語，台灣都係叫春聯，但依家好少人識。"},{"pid":"3bf25cf767856df4ee4bca2ee73e8926a0b1e3d2","tid":1831969,"uid":344847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4f782c985252465d9d59e4fdd23b3c6238a8458","tid":1831969,"uid":312858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T01:25:59.000Z","msg":"一人一句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鼠年光復百業<br />\n子歲香港封登"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T01:29:23.000Z","msg":"好句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望多啲巴絲參與創作"},{"pid":"58062171b0e3dcaf4ed7aa9cb5534f981e0637e0","tid":1831969,"uid":14478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T04:26:35.000Z","msg":"驅除共黨 光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fcc1e6733a64c8d010e8704b26fc48427bdb1e8","tid":1831969,"uid":344847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco